  <num>21-514</num>
  <heading>Release of patients hospitalized under section 21-513.</heading>
  <text>Unless proceedings for hospitalization under court order have been initiated under <cite path="21|5|IV">subchapter IV of this chapter</cite>, a hospital, upon the written request of a patient hospitalized pursuant to section 21-513  , shall immediately release him.</text>
